OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778695868
OL,3,CMarket concerns intensify as
OL,4,CWestminster descends into chaos again
OL,6,F"The timing is awful," Dales said.
OL,7,F"The war in Iran has already pushed up
OL,8,Finflation and mortgage rates. This
OL,9,Fwill supercharge that squeeze on
OL,10,Fhouseholds. Now mortgage rates look
OL,11,Fset to rise further due to domestic
OL,12,Fpolitical uncertainty."
OL,14,FFor many years, successive governments
OL,15,Fhave spent more than they have raised
OL,16,Fin tax and relied on investors -
OL,17,Fpension funds, banks, insurers and
OL,18,Foverseas buyers - to lend the money
OL,19,Fneeded to fund the difference.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
