OL,3,CMarket concerns intensify as
OL,4,CWestminster descends into chaos again
OL,6,FBorrowing surged during Covid. The
OL,7,FUK's national debt is now high by
OL,8,Fhistorical standards, and the
OL,9,Fconsequence is that the government now
OL,10,Fspends more than #100 billion a year
OL,11,Fservicing its interest costs.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe government is not "in hock" to the
OL,19,Fbond markets in quite the way Burnham
OL,20,Fsuggests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
